	    	<H3>Statup Options</H3>
	    	<ul>
	    		<li>
	    		<H5>Extent: </H5>To start at a certain extent add this to the url:
		    	<%=app%>/index.aspx?extent=xmin,ymin,xmax,ymax<br>
		    	where xmin,ymin,xmax,ymax are numbers in NAD83 zone 13 projection or longitude, latitude WGS 84 decimal degrees.<br>
	  			To specify the extent in another projection add &prj=projection #.<br>
	    		Examples: 
	    			<ul>
	    				<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?extent=395612,4519265,513379,4462957 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to an extent using the default projection of NAD83 zone 13)</li>
	    				<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?extent=714030,4200330,810030,4305000&prj=26912 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to an extent using the specified projection)</li>
		    			<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?extent=-103.56,39.21,-103.95,40.1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to an extent using lat long projection)</li>	    	
		    		</ul>
	    		</li>
	    		<li><h5>Label and Zoom to a Place Name or Point: </h5>To zoom into a location add this to the url:
		    	<%=app%>/index.aspx?place=location name or point<br>
		    	Use %20 in place of space if calling it from another website.<br>
	    		<u>Place Examples:</u>
	    			<ul>
	    				<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?place=Fort Collins&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to the specified location)</li>
	    				<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?place=Larimer County &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to the specified county)</li>
		    			<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?place=gmu 2 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to Game Management Unit 2)</li>
		    			<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?place=Wellington SWA&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to specified State Wildlife Area)</li>
						<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?place=Adams STL&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to specified State Trust Land)</li>
						<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?place=Rifle Falls SFU&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to specified State Fishing Unit)</li>
					</ul>
				<u>Point Examples:</u>
					<ul>
	    				<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?place=37.4015,-103.25 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to a latitude, longitude in decimal degrees)</li>
						<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?place=37:30:15,-103:25:41 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to a latitude, longitude in degrees, minutes, seconds)</li>
						<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?place=37:54.256,-103:44.21 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to a latitude, longitude in degrees, decimal minutes)</li>
	    				<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?place=300000,4200000 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to a point in default projection UTM NAD83 zone13)</li>
						<li><%=app%>/index.aspx?place=1142407,4518281&prj=26912 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(zooms to a point in the specified projection)</li>
						<ul>
						Some example projections (prj=####) are listed below:
						<ul>
							4326 &nbsp;= WGS 1984 lat long<br>
							26712 = UTM NAD 1927 Zone 12N<br>
							26713 = UTM NAD 1927 Zone 13N<br>
							26912 = UTM NAD 1983 Zone 12N<br>
							26913 = UTM NAD 1983 Zone 13N<br>
							32612 = UTM WGS 1984 Zone 12N<br>
							32613 = UTM WGS 1984 Zone 13N<br>
