			<li><H5>Custom MapService</H5>
	  		To zoom to a place in a custom map service, add this to the end of the url:<br>
	    		<%=app%>/index.aspx?map=[your custom map service]&field=[your field name]&value=[your value]<br/><br/>
				
				For example zoom to a zip code area using Esri's USA Zip Codes mapservice:<br/>
				&nbsp;&nbsp;<%=app%>/index.aspx?map=http://services.arcgis.com/P3ePLMYs2RVChkJx/arcgis/rest/services/<br/>
